ra2018a\">{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2018/6/14/17462944/final-fantasy-vii-remake-tetsuya-nomoura-kingdom-hearts-3-delay|title=Kingdom Hearts III's director says he's putting equal effort into Final Fantasy VII Remake|last=Farokhmanesh|first=Megan|work=[[The Verge]]|publisher=[[Vox Media]]|date=June 14, 2018|accessdate=June 15, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614195546/https://www.theverge.com/2018/6/14/17462944/final-fantasy-vii-remake-tetsuya-nomoura-kingdom-hearts-3-delay|archivedate=June 14, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Nomura2018b\">{{cite web|url=https://www.vg247.com/2018/06/15/final-fantasy-7-remake-e3-2018/|title=The Final Fantasy 7 remake skipped E3, but it's still in active development|last=O'Conner|first=James|work=[[VG247]]|publisher=VG247|date=June 15, 2018|accessdate=June 15, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615073816/https://www.vg247.com/2018/06/15/final-fantasy-7-remake-e3-2018/|archivedate=June 15, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RemakeSoP\">{{cite web|url=https://blog.us.playstation.com/2019/05/09/a-new-look-at-final-fantasy-vii-remake/|title=A New Look at Final Fantasy VII Remake|last=Kitase|first=Yoshinori|work=[[PlayStation Blog]]|publisher=[[PlayStation]]|date=May 9, 2019|accessdate=May 10, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510002108/https://blog.us.playstation.com/2019/05/09/a-new-look-at-final-fantasy-vii-remake/|archivedate=May 10, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"2020REL\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/06/10/final-fantasy-vii-remake-release-date-announced-e3-2019|title=Final Fantasy VII Remake Release Date Announced - E3 2019|first=Jonathan|last=Dornbush|date=June 9, 2019|publisher=[[Ziff Davis]]|work=[[IGN]]|accessdate=June 10, 2019|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610042558/https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/06/10/final-fantasy-vii-remake-release-date-announced-e3-2019|archivedate=June 10, 2019|url-status=live}}