 at the Speed of Sound]]'' <br />{{small|(Wings)}}\n|\n*Released: 25 March 1976\n*Label: Capitol\n|2\n|2\n|1\n|32\n|4\n|3\n|2\n|2\n|7\n|1\n|\n*UK: Gold<ref name=\"bpi\" />\n*FRA: Gold<ref name=\"InfoDiscCert2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.infodisc.fr/Certif_Album.php |title=French albums certifications |publisher=[[InfoDisc]] |accessdate=8 November 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100621054859/http://www.infodisc.fr/Certif_Album.php |archivedate=21 June 2010 }} Note: See \"WINGS\"</ref>\n*US: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|''[[London Town (Wings album)|London Town]]'' <br />{{small|(Wings)}}\n|\n*Released: 31 March 1978\n*Label: [[Parlophone]] {{small|(Worldwide)}}<br />Capitol {{small|(US)}}\n|4\n|3\n|3\n|6\n|4\n|1\n|2\n|4\n|4\n|2\n|\n*UK: Gold<ref name=\"bpi\" />\n*FRA: Gold<ref name=\"InfoDiscCert2\" />\n*GER: Gold<ref name=musik>{{cite certification|region=Germany|accessdate=20 September 2009|artist=Wings}}</ref>\n*NLD: Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nvpi.nl/nvpi-audio/marktinformatie/goud-platina/|title=Goud/Platina|website=nvpi.nl}}</ref>\n*US: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|''[[Back to the Egg]]'' <br />{{small|(Wings)}}\n|\n*Released: 8 June 1979\n*Label: Parlophone {{small|(worldwide)}}<br />[[Columbia Records|Columbia]] {{small|(North America)}}\n|6\n|3\n|11 \n|16\n|7\n|11\n|5\n|9\n|5\n|8\n|\n*UK: Gold<ref name=\"bpi\" />\n*CAN: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"CRIA2\" />\n*US: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|''[[McCartney II]]''\n|\n*Released: 16 May 1980\n*Label: Parlophone {{small|(worldwide)}}<br />[[Columbia Records|Columbia]] {{small|(North America)}}\n|1\n|6\n|2\n|19\n|8\n|11\n|5\n|5\n|5\n|3\n|\n*UK: Gold<ref name=\"bpi2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bpi.co.uk/certifiedawards/search.aspx |title=Certified Awards Search |publisher=[[British Phonographic Industry]] |accessdate=19 August 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090924015932/http: